summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Milwaukee Land Company to certain lands in the southwest quarter (SW 1/4) of Section Thirty-four (34), Township Twenty-three (23) North, Range Eight (8) East, W. M. in Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating Eighty-seven and Seventy-five One-hundredths Dollars ($87.75) from Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund for the payment for said lands.
